snippet.title: Johnny Depp Cut Off Part Of Finger During Drunken Rage
snippet.description:
On Monday, TMZ published images of a nasty injury Johnny Depp had last year during a drunken shouting match with Amber Heard. According to spokespeople for the actress, the injury occurred when the newlyweds were staying at a villa in Australia. Depp, allegedly drunk and high on ecstasy, raged around, breaking bottles and windows, and then ruined a plastic phone. In the process, he cut off a chunk of his forefinger. This new report and the published photos come only days after a video was released in which Depp is seen smashing bottles, slamming around a kitchen and criticizing Heard.
